snippet.title: DAY OF RECKONING | Can Humanity Survive the Next Invasion? | Full Movie
snippet.description:
Years after a global collapse, the threat returns.
Survival now depends on those willing to stand and fight back.

Fifteen years after mysterious creatures emerged from another realm and nearly wiped out humanity, the world struggles to rebuild. Survivors have learned to adapt, but peace is short-lived when the forces responsible begin to rise again. As the threat resurfaces, a new group of fighters must step forward to protect what remains of mankind and face a battle that could decide the future of the planet.

Director: Joel Novoa
Cast: Barbara Crampton, Hana Hayes, Heather McComb, Jackson Hurst, Nick Gomez, Raymond Barry.
